{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T11:50:06.126Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Scaled Dot-Product Attention — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What Scaled Dot-Product Attention Is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scaled Dot-Product Attention"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the fundamental attention mechanism behind Transformers that computes attention weights by taking "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "dot products between Query (Q) and Key (K) vectors"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to measure alignment, then "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "scaling"}, {"type": "text", "text": " those dot products by dividing by "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " before applying softmax. It's the core mechanism used in the original \"Attention Is All You Need\" paper that introduced Transformers."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why Scaled Dot-Product Attention Matters in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This mechanism is essential because it:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Capability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Impact"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Computes relevance"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Measures similarity between words/tokens in a sequence"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Enables parallelization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "All tokens processed simultaneously (unlike RNNs)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Captures long-range dependencies"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Any token can attend to any other token"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Stable training"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaling prevents vanishing gradients in deep Transformers"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Foundation for modern models"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Powers ChatGPT, DALL·E, Midjourney, and all Transformer-based AI"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Scaled Dot-Product Attention Works (4-Step Process)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The mechanism works through four clear steps:"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Formula:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\text{Attention}(Q, K, V) = \\text{softmax}\\left(\\frac{QK^{T}}{\\sqrt{d_k}}\\right)V"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "Q"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = Query matrix (size: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "K"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = Key matrix (size: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "V"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = Value matrix (size: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_v"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = Dimension of key/query vectors\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = Sequence length"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step 1: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Compare"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Dot Product)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Take one token as query and compare it against all keys using dot products"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Input: \"I love AI\"\nEmbeddings converted to Q, K, V matrices\n\nStep 1: Compute similarity\n  Q × K^T = Compatibility Matrix\n\nExample for \"I\":\n  Q(\"I\") · K(\"I\") = 0.5  (similarity with itself)\n  Q(\"I\") · K(\"love\") = 0.8  (similarity with \"love\")\n  Q(\"I\") · K(\"AI\") = 0.3  (similarity with \"AI\")\n  \nResult: [0.5, 0.8, 0.3] (raw similarity scores)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This gives a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "grid of similarity scores: every query against every key"}, {"type": "text", "text": ". The dot product measures how similar the query is to each key."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step 2: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scale"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Divide by "}, {"type": "text", "text": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Divide those scores by "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " to keep the values numerically stable"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Raw scores: [0.5, 0.8, 0.3]\nDimension: d_k = 512 (common in Transformers)\nScaling factor: 1/√512 ≈ 1/22.6 ≈ 0.044\n\nScaled scores: [0.5×0.044, 0.8×0.044, 0.3×0.044]\n             = [0.022, 0.035, 0.013]"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why scaling is critical"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Without Scaling"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "With Scaling"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Variance"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Dot product variance = "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (grows with dimension)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Variance = 1 (constant)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Softmax behavior"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "\"Winner-take-all\": extreme probabilities (1.0, 0.0, 0.0)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Balanced probabilities (0.4, 0.35, 0.25)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vanishing gradients (near 0)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Substantial gradients for learning"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Mathematical reason"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": If "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "q"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " and "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " are "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "-dimensional vectors with mean 0 and variance 1, their dot product has mean 0 and variance "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ". Dividing by "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " brings variance back to 1."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step 3: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Normalize"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Apply Softmax)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Apply softmax to turn raw scores into a probability distribution—values between 0 and 1 that sum to 1"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaled scores: [0.022, 0.035, 0.013]\n\nSoftmax calculation:\n  exp(0.022) = 1.022\n  exp(0.035) = 1.036\n  exp(0.013) = 1.013\n  Sum = 3.071\n\nAttention weights:\n  w₁ = 1.022/3.071 = 0.33 (33%)\n  w₂ = 1.036/3.071 = 0.34 (34%)\n  w₃ = 1.013/3.071 = 0.33 (33%)\n  \nResult: [0.33, 0.34, 0.33] (attention weights summing to 1)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Softmax "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "normalizes the scores across all keys for a given query"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", ensuring attention weights sum to 1. These are the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "attention weights"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that determine how much to focus on each token."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step 4: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Combine"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Weighted Sum of Values)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use those weights to compute a weighted sum of the values"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Attention weights: [0.33, 0.34, 0.33]\nValue vectors:\n  V(\"I\") = [0.1, 0.9, 0.2, ...]\n  V(\"love\") = [0.8, 0.2, 0.5, ...]\n  V(\"AI\") = [0.3, 0.6, 0.8, ...]\n\nWeighted sum:\n  Output = 0.33×V(\"I\") + 0.34×V(\"love\") + 0.33×V(\"AI\")\n         = [0.41, 0.56, 0.52, ...]\n         \nResult: New representation of \"I\" that incorporates context from \"love\" and \"AI\""}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each output token becomes a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "linear combination of all previous tokens"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—maybe 37% from one, 23% from another, and a little from the rest."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Complete Process Visually"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Input Sequence: [Token₁, Token₂, Token₃]\n\n↓ Linear layers with weights W_Q, W_K, W_V\n\nQ = [Q₁, Q₂, Q₃]  (Queries)\nK = [K₁, K₂, K₃]  (Keys)\nV = [V₁, V₂, V₃]  (Values)\n\n↓ Step 1: Dot Product\nQ × K^T = [[score₁₁, score₁₂, score₁₃],\n           [score₂₁, score₂₂, score₂₃],\n           [score₃₁, score₃₂, score₃₃]]\n\n↓ Step 2: Scale\nDivide by √d_k\n[[score₁₁/√d_k, score₁₂/√d_k, ...], ...]\n\n↓ Step 3: Softmax\nNormalize rows to sum = 1\n[[0.3, 0.5, 0.2],\n [0.4, 0.1, 0.5],\n [0.2, 0.3, 0.5]] (Attention Matrix)\n\n↓ Step 4: Weighted Sum\nAttention Matrix × V\nOutput = [[output₁], [output₂], [output₃]]\n\nFinal result: Each token's new representation incorporates context from all tokens"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Q, K, V: The Three Components"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Component"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Role"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Size"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Query (Q)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What we're looking for"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_k"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key (K)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What we're searching against"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_k"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Value (V)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Content to extract when matched"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times d_v"}}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "**"}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_q = d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": ": Query and Key dimensions must match for dot product"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "**"}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_v"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": ": Value dimension can differ (determines output dimension)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Analogy"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Query"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Your search query (\"best pizza\")\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Database of items to search through (\"pizza\", \"restaurant\", \"food\")\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Value"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Actual content of matching items (detailed menu, reviews)"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits of Scaled Dot-Product Attention"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefit"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Numerical stability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaling prevents dot products from growing too large"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Stable gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Keeps softmax inputs in regime where gradients are substantial"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Prevents peaky attention"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Prevents attention from becoming overly concentrated on single input"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Efficient computation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Matrix operations can be parallelized on GPUs"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Enables deep models"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Essential for training deep Transformer models"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade-offs & Limitations"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limitation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Computational complexity"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "O(n^{2} \\times d)"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " quadratic in sequence length"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memory intensive"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Attention matrix size = "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n \\times n"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (large for long sequences)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scaling factor fixed"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " works well but may need tuning for extreme dimensions"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of scaled dot-product attention as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "library search system"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Step 1 (Compare)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You have a query (\"science fiction books\") and compare it against all book titles (keys)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Step 2 (Scale)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You normalize the similarity scores so they're not too extreme"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Step 3 (Normalize)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You convert scores to probabilities (80% match for \"dystopian novels\", 20% for \"space exploration\")"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Step 4 (Combine)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You retrieve the actual book content (values) weighted by those probabilities"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The result is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "weighted summary"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of all relevant books, not just the single best match."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Or think of it as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "team meeting"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each person is a token in the sequence"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Query"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"What do I need to contribute?\""}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"What is everyone else saying?\""}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Dot product"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Measure alignment between your contribution and others'"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scale"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Don't overreact to extreme opinions"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Softmax"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Convert alignments to attention weights (who to listen to most)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Combine"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Create your final response based on weighted input from everyone"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Scaled Dot-Product Attention"}, {"type": "text", "text": " formula: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\text{Attention}(Q, K, V) = \\text{softmax}\\left(\\frac{QK^{T}}{\\sqrt{d_k}}\\right)V"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "4-step process"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Compare (dot product) → Scale (divide by "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ") → Normalize (softmax) → Combine (weighted sum)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Why scaling is critical"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Dot product variance = "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "d_k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", which grows with dimension; dividing by "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{d_k}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " brings variance back to 1"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Without scaling"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Softmax becomes \"winner-take-all\" (extreme 1.0, 0.0, 0.0 probabilities) causing vanishing gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "With scaling"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Softmax produces balanced probabilities (0.4, 0.35, 0.25) enabling stable training"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Q, K, V components"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Query (what we seek), Key (what we search), Value (content to extract)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Massively parallelizable"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": All tokens processed simultaneously, unlike sequential RNNs"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Foundation of Transformers"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Powers all modern generative AI (ChatGPT, DALL·E, Midjourney)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scaled Dot-Product Attention is the core mechanism that enables Transformers to understand context and relationships in sequences, making it the backbone of modern generative AI."}]}]}}